data.title: Parking Rates
data.meta_description: Find out how much it costs to park at downtown parking garages, metered spaces and surface lots including daytime, evening, event, monthly and disabled parking rates.
data.text:
Event Parking Rates

Event parking rates may be in effect at select locations when there is a large event in downtown Orlando or at a downtown venue.

Garages are $10 with the exception of the GEICO parking garage. Lots are $10, with the exception of the Grove Park Lot.

You can also pay in advance to reserve a parking space. Additional fees may apply for pre-purchased parking through Ticketmaster and Parkmobile.

Reserve and Purchase Event Parking
